```{.r .cell-code}
png(filename = "p1.png",
    width = 6,
    height = 6,
    units = "in",
    res = 300)

ggplot(data = PlantGrowth,
       mapping = aes(x = group,
                     y = weight,
                     fill = group)) +
  
geom_violin(width = 1,
            alpha = 0.2) +
  
geom_boxplot(width = 0.3, 
             color = "black",
             alpha = 0.2)

dev.off()
```
